Wide Thought Host (WTH)
Copyright 2026 The Wide Thought Host contributors

This product is an independent, community-maintained distribution derived from
Gork Build (https://github.com/thedavidweng/gork-build), with vendor telemetry
and branding removed. WTH extends the foundation with multi-backend LLM support,
enhanced agent reasoning, and improved TUI.

